ODM had imprisoned Budalang&rsquo;i MP Ababu Namwamba (pictured) and he was not free to conduct activities beneficial to residents, LPK constituency manager Godfrey Obayi has said.But he is now at ease to undertake his responsibility in the Labour Party of Kenya and free to do what he feels will be beneficial to Budalang&rsquo;i constituents and the people of Western, Obayi said.He spoke to LPK supporters at Sirimba, Namalo, Ruambwa and Munani trading centres in Bunyala North ward on Wednesday.